title: rom name
content:
local lastRomName = ""

while true do
    local romName = gameinfo.getromname()

    if romName ~= lastRomName then
        lastRomName = romName
        print("New ROM detected: " .. romName)

        local file = io.open("current_game.txt", "w")
        if file then
            file:write(romName)
            file:close()
        else
            print("Error opening file for writing.")
        end
    end

    emu.frameadvance()
end
